<head>CONCRETE</head><list type="translations"><item xml:lang="zh">具體</item></list>
<div type="definition">
<p>OBJECT which CAN be PERCEIVED by ORGANS of PERCEIVE:perception.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>Shí 實 (ant. xū 虛 insubstantial, abstract) refers to something being manifest and concrete rather than abstract.</p></div></div>
